      "module_path": "dry_check::config",
      "docs": "Filesystem DTO for `.harness/config/dry-check.json` after the final schema_version 3 migration. Existing threshold is preserved; new fields added in this track are max_parallelism (D3 schema_version 2), fast_reasoning_effort (D4 schema_version 3), final_reasoning_effort (D4 schema_version 3), known_bad_injection_rate_percent (D4 schema_version 3), and known_bad_detection_threshold_percent (D4 schema_version 3). Raw primitive fields are used here because this is the serde boundary; the loader validates fast_reasoning_effort/final_reasoning_effort and the composition layer converts numeric settings to the validated usecase::DryCheckConfig (DryCheckPercent / DryCheckParallelism newtype wrappers). CN-06/CN-04.",
