      "module_path": "dry_check::codex_dry_checker",
      "docs": "Secondary adapter implementing the tier-aware DryCheckAgentPort. Updated for D4 two-tier execution: Fast uses the fast_model from CapabilityConfigDto plus fast_reasoning_effort from dry-check.json; Final uses the primary model plus final_reasoning_effort from dry-check.json. The adapter executes exactly one production/probe pair on the tier requested by DryCheckJudgeTier and does not accept or reject run-level calibration; DryCheckInteractor uses DryCheckConfig percentages for probe count, detection threshold, and all-pair final retry. Private fields hold model and reasoning-effort configuration for tier execution.",
